{"id": 3064, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你觉得自己生活的哪部分正在被“算法化”？", "description": "我不再是我，而是许许多多数据的组合。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 5792, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191119000134qTlFXR9A6CHepPSG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-18T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6050, "title": "现如今你觉得自己生活的哪部分正在被“算法化”？", "content": "你觉得自己生活的哪部分好像正在被“算法化”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349537, "content": "手机成为身体外接设备，工作生活都可以被精确量化", "image": "img/option/option/20191118232756uEoCVtR9wzUsaxZ2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349538, "content": "喜好、行为和观点都能被收集分析，成为广告的目标", "image": "img/option/option/20191118233404ouyd9XKrcsmBMLAp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349539, "content": "注意力被热点长期占据，大脑变成互联网的线下终端", "image": "img/option/option/20191118233552DxdLEj2B7Gz9n5ZJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349540, "content": "动动手指就能自制线上舒适区，过滤掉一切不喜欢的", "image": "img/option/option/201911182342177pIgrwfT8VQA2lcz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349541, "content": "对“用户/流量/人群”之类贴在自己身上的标签习以为常", "image": "img/option/option/20191118234659wyNFbBT3OWQS8nl9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349542, "content": "“流行”的套路越来越相似，走到哪都是复读机/复印机", "image": "img/option/option/20191118234752P7Yutk561shi8Abq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349543, "content": "越来越分不出机器和真人的差别（比如 AI 合成的人脸", "image": "img/option/option/20191118235258sCYQLuy10ejZvh7R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349544, "content": "生活方式也开始像算法一样，总想再高效/优化一点", "image": "img/option/option/20191118235242DercG1JL8nBFf9wa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349545, "content": "我暂时还行，并没有遇到这种谜思", "image": "img/option/option/20191119000537Xk9G3BsWHMDnE8lY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}